  "body": "Any normal messenger that supports images will support also pasting images into chat from clipboard.\r\n\r\nThis is also a crucial feature for collaboration because it makes it easy to show people things without having to go through the tedious process of saving screenshots first as files and then navigating to them.\r\n\r\nAcceptance Criteria:\r\n- on the browser, right click on an image and choose copy image, then go to the desktop app and in the chat input, do ctrl +v. the image should be pasted as an attachment",
